{"tid":764578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有輕鐵站沉降　無交代幅度","createTime":"2018-08-02T05:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T11:12:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaaee9e20ce16bd9e802d1527ded9b54d2f0329","tid":764578,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20466843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20466843&d=y9KBTwxd%2BVFK6stHYWMMTosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=228f9edf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20466843&h=0ef87146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20466843</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02日 <br />\n<br />\n再有輕鐵站沉降　無交代幅度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180802/large/0801tat0101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F0801tat0101.jpg&h=45cdeef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】多個港鐵車站相繼出現沉降，毗鄰新鴻基地盤的屯門泳池輕鐵站（圖）亦有同樣情況。港鐵承認去年底已留意到該站出現輕微沉降，幅度一直平穩，未達停工指標，該站仍符安全標準。有區議員認為港鐵應公佈實際幅度，釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n屯門區議會交通及運輸委員會副主席葉文斌稱，本周一有居民向他反映輕鐵屯門泳池站出現大量港鐵人員，「最少有6、7車」，疑似正在量度路軌位置，居民擔心該站沉降。他遂向港鐵查詢，惟未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地盤大部份打樁已完成<br />\n<br />\n港鐵昨接受《蘋果》查詢時，始承認去年年底已留意到屯門泳池輕鐵站2號月台出現輕微沉降，幅度一直平穩，維持在屋宇署的20毫米停工標準內，而該站月台結構、路軌及鐵路設施符合安全標準，未有回應沉降幅度為何。港鐵續指，有關地盤工程屬鐵路保護範圍內，據其了解該地盤大部份地基打樁工程已完成，正進行上蓋建造工程，若沉降達停工標準，會按機制要求發展商停工。<br />\n<br />\n葉指政府早前指共有64個監察沉降地點，惟一直未有詳情，促政府全數公佈，並告知居民對鄰近地區的影響。葉指將於區議會提出質詢。本報向新鴻基查詢，截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者趙雅婷  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n學者倡全日制幼園單親優先<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n勝和掀運菜風雲逼警開槍　瘋駕青年中彈落網拒爆同黨下落"},{"pid":"9ba2c33f60f9a62e0278f7a34285f78cc89e1c02","tid":764578,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb39c9ddfd007fc66d40340fc3aff343aa2be4db","tid":764578,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok啦"}]}